@node "sx" "SX Online functions"

 @{b}@{bg shine}System-X (eSSeXX)@{ub}@{bg back}

 Here are some more informations about the things, 
 are happened @{b}online@{ub}:

 @{"ĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀAlterĀFlags" link "sx_flaglist" 0} - the File Flaglist                       
 @{"ĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀAnsi/Ascii" link "sx_ansasc" 0} - general info`s                       
 @{"ĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀAquaScan" link "sx_aqua" 0} - some words for aquaScan
 @{"ĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀBulletins" link "sx_bulls" 0} - the Bulletins directory
 @{"ĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀChat" link "sx_chat" 0} - force user to chat
 @{"ĀĀĀĀĀCommentToSysop" link "sx_comment" 0} - write a comment direct to the Sysop
 @{"ĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀConferences" link "sx_confs" 0} - how to handle the Conferences
 @{"ĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀĀDownload" link "sx_download" 0} - different forms of Downloads
